    "content": "<p>This is how Trans people are most often showcased where I'm from in Ohio, Kentucky, and Indiana media. I have tried and failed to imagine a BIPOC Trans Woman being this deliberately provocative. Regardless of whether or not it should matter, Cis or Het gender teacher, to do something like this at a time when Trans folk are under attack is tone-deaf at the least. <a href=\"https://local12.com/news/nation-world/canadian-school-threatens-students-with-suspension-if-they-photograph-trans-teacher-parents-say-canada-transgenger-giant-prosthetic-breasts-kayla-lemieux-oakville-trafalgar-high-halton-disctrict-board\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"ellipsis\">local12.com/news/nation-world/</span><span class=\"invisible\">canadian-school-threatens-students-with-suspension-if-they-photograph-trans-teacher-parents-say-canada-transgenger-giant-prosthetic-breasts-kayla-lemieux-oakville-trafalgar-high-halton-disctrict-board</span></a></p>",
